body_html:
The only test that appears to be failing is the goldens tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test which passes locally. As per the jenkins stdout, I ran:

    $ bazel build tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test
    $ bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test \
          --update_goldens True

but this did not appear to alter any files.

body:
The only test that appears to be failing is the goldens tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test which passes locally. As per the jenkins stdout, I ran:

```
    $ bazel build tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test
    $ bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test \
          --update_goldens True
```

but this did not appear to alter any files.
